Authorization: {{token}}


### ✅ GET Galeri Default (Foto, halaman 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/galeri?jenis_media=Foto&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ GET Galeri Video + search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/galeri?jenis_media=Video&search=perayaan&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}